es.csic.iiia.nsm.norm.evaluation

Class NormComplianceOutcomes

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.csic.iiia.nsm.norm.evaluation.NormComplianceOutcomes

  • public class NormComplianceOutcomes
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing information about the norms that each agent has fulfilled/infringed, and the agent contexts in which those norms are applicable. Furthermore, the class has information about the number of conflicts that arose after agents fulfilled/infringed the norms
    Author:
    "Javier Morales (jmorales@iiia.csic.es)"

      • getCompliance

        public java.util.List<NormCompliance> getCompliance(Norm norm)
        Returns a List of compliance actions for a given norm. That is, if the norm has been fulfilled (namely the norm exists in the list of all fulfilled norms), it returns a list with the compliance action "Compliance". If the norm has also been infringed, the returned list will also contain "Infringement"
        Parameters:
        norm - the norm
        Returns:
        a List of compliance actions for a given norm
        See Also:
        NormCompliance
